ignage as per SANS 1185/6.</li>\r\n	<li>Accident Investigations.</li>\r\n	<li>Liaison with Regulatory parties namely Department of Labour, Compensation Commissioner, The Federated Mutual Assurance Fund.</li>\r\n	<li>Interpretation of all SHE Legislation and keeping clients informed of change in Legislation and the impact thereof.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nClients have stayed with us for more than 9 years due to the fact that we add real value to their SHE Programme and are on the cutting edge with the latest SHE trends and information.\r\n\r\nThe effective implementation of the Safety, Health &amp; Environmental (SHE) management systems has offered Frontlines clients above average returns and results have shown a rapid and sustained reduction in incident occurrence as well as financial savings on their annual assessment by the Compensation Commissioner and The Federated Employers Mutual Assurance Company Limited.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_empty_space height=\"32px\"][rev_slider_vc alias=\"she\"][vc_empty_space height=\"32px\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Safety, Health & Environmental (SHE) Consulting','','publish','open','open','','safety-health-environmental-she-consulting','','','2015-04-22 14:18:09','2015-04-22 12:18:09','',213,'http://192.168.1.11/FRONTLINE/website/htdocs/?page_id=223',0,'page','',0),(224,1,'2015-04-21 15:03:13','2015-04-21 13:03:13','[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]Frontline has successfully over the last 10 years establish ourselves as a leader in the Risk Management Solutions in the area of Safety, Health and Environmental (SHE) compliance.\r\n\r\nWe have a holistic approach and normally start with a comprehensive SHE Legal Audit/Walk-about to identify potential SHE hazards.\r\n\r\nOnce the specific hazards have been identified, we offer the following solutions:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Guidance in a cost effective Implication Programme to ensure that all identified hazards are evaluated and controll